User Story

    First Steps
        Show categories in sidebar
        Clicking category open items in main
        Clicking item adds it to cart
        Cart div hidden until items added

    Phase Two
        Worker
            Can select category to view items
            Can add items to cart
            Can open and close tabs
            
            Late game
                Can customize their layout

        Manager
            Can add and remove categories and items
            Can alter items
            Can keep inventory

            Late game
                Can alter what certain users see (bar/floor)

